# Normalize every text file to LF on all platforms. The conformance suite
# compares rendered output against testdata/**/expected.out byte for byte, so a
# CRLF checkout on Windows would fail those comparisons; forcing LF keeps the
# fixtures, gofmt'd sources, and generated Go identical on Windows, macOS, and
# Linux. text=auto still leaves any binary file untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
